entry.name: AstraMilitarumBroken1
entry.value: "他们正在消灭我们! 我们无法进行反击!"

entry.name: AstraMilitarumBroken4
entry.value: "快跑伙计们, 希望被别政委发现了!"

entry.name: AstraMilitarumShaken0
entry.value: "可以祈祷吗? 噢, 帝皇, 噢 基里曼, 保佑我们. "

entry.name: AstraMilitarumShaken1
entry.value: "噢, 见鬼. 能不能来点儿给力的武器?"

entry.name: AstraMilitarumShaken3
entry.value: "我们留下来必然会死. 但如果逃跑, 将军会把我们枪毙!"

entry.name: AstraMilitarumShaken4
entry.value: "鼓起勇气, 伙计们, 鼓起勇气. "

entry.name: NecronsBroken2
entry.value: "我们的单位已分散. 撤退."

entry.name: NecronsBroken3
entry.value: "你的命令不可能完成, 大人."

entry.name: NecronsShaken3
entry.value: "The Triarchs did not brief us on this."

entry.name: OrksBroken1
entry.value: "I fink I remembered something in my digs... back soon!"

entry.name: OrksShaken3
entry.value: "我得来点儿真菌啤酒压压惊."

entry.name: SpaceMarinesShaken0
entry.value: "冲破黑暗, 我们必将获得胜利."

entry.name: SpaceMarinesShaken1
entry.value: "我... 相信帝皇. 为了信仰!"

entry.name: SpaceMarinesShaken2
entry.value: "我是坚不可破的护盾, 我为抵抗黑暗而生."

entry.name: SpaceMarinesShaken3
entry.value: "...blessed is the mind too small for doubt."

entry.name: SpaceMarinesShaken4
entry.value: "Whilst our enemies draw breath, we cannot afford fear."
